apihelp-visualeditor-description: Mopohuwalingo HTML5 ode halaman lonto layanan parsoid.
apihelp-visualeditor-param-basetimestamp: To'u molahu, aaturuwa nilai botiye mowali wakutu to sa'ati boli'a botiya pilohutu. Mopohunalo modeteksi konflik momoli'o.
apihelp-visualeditor-param-html: HTML u molawo ode Parsoid u mengkonversi mowali teks wiki.
apihelp-visualeditor-param-oldid: Nomoro boli'a u otohilawo (secara baku: versi pulitiyo).
apihelp-visualeditor-param-pst: Pra-molahu momoli'o teks wiki to'udiipo ode Parsoid (paction=parsefragment).
apihelp-visualeditor-param-starttimestam: To'u molahu, aaturuwa nilai botiye mowali wakutu to sa'ati boli'a botiya diletohu. Mopohunalo modeteksi konflik momoli'o.
apihelp-visualeditor-param-wikitext: Teks wiki u molawo ode Parsoid u mengkonversi mowali HTML (paction=parsefragment).
apihelp-visualeditoredit-description: Tahuwa halaman HTML5 ode MediaWiki (konversiyolo mowali teks wiki melalui layanan Parsoid).

apihelp-visualeditoredit-param-cachekey: Popohunawa hasili lonto hihile serializeforcache wolo u'unti botiya to'udiipo. Modeehu $1html.
apihelp-visualeditoredit-param-captchaid: ID Captcha (to'u molahu wolo respons captcha).

apihelp-visualeditoredit-param-html: HTML u molawo ode Parsoid u molulu'a teks wiki.
